Generate internal/apperror/apperror.go for a Go service.
Requirements: - Sentinels: ErrNotFound, ErrConflict, ErrUnauthorized, ErrForbidden, ErrInvalidInput, ErrUnavailable, ErrInternal - AppError struct {Op, Code string; Err error} with Error() and Unwrap() - HTTPStatus(err error) int — returns 404/409/401/403/400/503/500 - GRPCCode(err error) codes.Code — same mapping for gRPC - Wrap(op string, err error) error — convenience helper - 100% test coverage in apperror_test.go using errors.Is and errors.As
Service name: {{SERVICE_NAME}}
